forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=44401803&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">skives 发表于 2019-07-05 21:59:20</font></a></div>2333333...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/saraba1st/id1221237470?mt=8\"><font color=\"#999999\">-- 来自 能搜索的 Stage1官方 iOS客户端</font></a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"16156","username":"cocoaghost","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"15864","dbdateline":"1562337794","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"44402661","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-7-5 23:13","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=44394723&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">傘木希美 发表于 2019-7-5 04:24</font></a><br />\r\n有这么胃疼吗</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" />如果你喜欢冈妈那一套（我指的是真实之泪那套）<br />\r\n那这剧还是可以看看的2333这漫画前半部分挺好的，冈妈对这个年纪的孩子的心态把握真的是非常纯熟，一点点的波动都能写得非常生动。当然原作画师的配合也是功不可没。<br />\r\n后半就是很冈式风格的那一套贵乱了，而且荒女的贵乱有点为乱而乱，强行矛盾的意思。当然我觉得在目前扭曲厨，败犬党盛行的观众届，这作品的话题性一定会相当高的。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"16157","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"15865","dbdateline":"1562339606","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"44402700","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"JustW","authorid":"511436","dateline":"2019-7-5 23:18","message":"<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/001.png\" />我感觉丽奈想要自己变得特别，完全没必要让所有人都想她一样特别啊，这样大家都特别了自己还能特别吗？唯一合理的解释就是丽奈那会儿“帮泷老师实现梦想”的想法已经盖过“我要变得特别”的想法了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/saraba1st/id1221237470?mt=8\"><font color=\"#999999\">-- 来自 有消息提醒的 Stage1官方 iOS客户端</font></a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"16158","username":"JustW","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"15866","dbdateline":"1562339895","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"44402712","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"magicyang1991","authorid":"409448","dateline":"2019-7-5 23:19","message":"高坂丽奈那句话让我觉得黄大叔对她几年的感情投入通通喂了狗","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"16159","username":"magicyang1991","adminid":"0","groupid":"31","memberstatus":"0","number":"15867","dbdateline":"1562339999","groupiconid":"7"},{"pid":"44402736","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-7-5 23:22","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=44382422&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">小糸ゆう 发表于 2019-7-4 05:32</font></a><br />\r\n小说的模式当然可以归类，但内容是无穷尽的。<br />\r\n书名比起小说的主要内容，和小说的特色关系更大。<br />\r\n另外你不 ...</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" />所以说我们是喜好上的偏差，这个没法调和的23333<br />\r\n在这个问题上我已经不想争执太多了2333，各取所需不好么<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/065.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"16160","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"15868","dbdateline":"1562340146","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"44402768","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"wuliaozheX","authorid":"389976","dateline":"2019-7-5 23:25","message":"冈妈的贵乱真的是为乱而乱。<br />\n真实之泪还好，起因经过结果，各个角色的逻辑勉强能理顺，除了我养鸡居然败了不可理喻只外没有太过分的地方<br />\n然后什么风平浪静就开始了，能多乱来多乱，人物为剧情服务<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/020.png\" />而且换汤不换药都是那一套<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/051.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n—— 来自 HUAWEI MHA-AL00, Android 9上的 <a href=\"https://github.com/ykrank/S1-Next/releases\">S1Next-鹅版</a> v2.1.2","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"16161","username":"wuliaozheX","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"15869","dbdateline":"1562340300","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"44402802","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-7-5 23:27","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=44402700&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">JustW 发表于 2019-7-5 15:18</font></a><br />\r\n我感觉丽奈想要自己变得特别，完全没必要让所有人都想她一样特别啊，这样大家都特别了自己还能特别 ...</div><br />\n“让大家都特别”（并不）<br />\r\n“刻苦训练，能夺金了”（正解）<br />\r\n不冲突不矛盾，别把小女孩想得太成熟，只是个十六七岁的少女而已，而且还是没经历过什么真正考验和磨难的少女，有点小执念很好懂。<br />\r\n当年丽奈能跑到千寻墓前起誓夺金，她今年就能这样执拗，性格使然。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"16162","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"15870","dbdateline":"1562340474","groupiconid":"8"}],"allowpostcomment":[],"comments":{"44398321":[]},"commentcount":{"44398321":null},"ppp":"30","setting_rewriterule":{"portal_topic":"topic-{name}.html","portal_article":"article-{id}-{page}.html","forum_forumdisplay":"forum-{fid}-{page}.html","forum_viewthread":"thread-{tid}-{page}-{prevpage}.html","group_group":"group-{fid}-{page}.html","home_space":"space-{user}-{value}.html","home_blog":"blog-{uid}-{blogid}.html","forum_archiver":"{action}-{value}.html","plugin":"{pluginid}-{module}.html"},"setting_rewritestatus":["portal_topic","portal_article","forum_forumdisplay","forum_viewthread","group_group","home_space","home_blog","forum_archiver","plugin"],"forum_threadpay":"","cache_custominfo_postno":["<sup>#</sup>","楼主",""],"forum":{"password":"0"}}}